 EMPLOYED THERE AS GUIDES AND IT IS    
 OPEN FROM 1400 TO 1700 HOURS.         
 THERE ARE 30,000 TO 40,000 VISITORS A 
 YEAR AND THE ADMISSION CHARGES        
